description
From: http://myeigenharp.wordpress.com/2013/3/27/octave-talker/
Octave talker, 
Originally I wanted to do this action on another keygroup, to allow me to switch between the two
This switch was done on a talker i happen to call ‘green talker’

script
empty join
green talker listen

1 called 1 cancel
'
empty join
octave talker listen
1 called 1 cancel
" main keygroup hey octave by 1 down " when 1 called 1 do
2 called 1 cancel
" main keygroup hey octave by 1 up " when 2 called 1 do
' when 1 called 1

2 called 1 cancel
'
empty join
octave talker listen
1 called 1 cancel
" main keygroup hey octave by 0.33333333333333331 down " when 1 called 1 do
2 called 1 cancel
" main keygroup hey octave by 0.33333333333333331 up " when 2 called 1 do
' when 2 called 1
